Benise is a world class musician, and this dvd features wonderful music as well as dance and productions. I enjoyed this so much that I immediately ordered more to give as gifts. I would recommend this dvd to anyone for entertainment purposes and to inspire oneself as well. I look forward to hearing more from this artist.
